<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="no-matter">no matter</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[与疑问词连用] 无论；不管：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You and I will always be friends, <strong>no matter what</strong> happens.
不管发生什么，你我永远是朋友。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>No matter how</strong> hard the rain falls and the wind blows, the police keep to their posts. 
无论雨多急、风多大，警察一直坚守在自己的岗位上。</p></div></div>